{"hash":"5c9f77c79d4cc646818b1144909cda2d85a837ab","data":{"subject":{"title":"NinjaTrader","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"Beta Release Notes - NinjaTrader 8 Help Guide","path":"/content/work/beta-release-notes-ninja-trader-8-help-guide/","date":"January 2017","timeToRead":1,"description":"Through the two-year beta release cycle of NinjaTrader 8, I was responsible for compiling and writing release notes that described the changes for each iteration up until the final release candidate.","content":"\n","cover_image":"/work/images/beta.png","company":"NinjaTrader LLC","tags":[{"id":"Technical writing","path":"/tag/Technical%20writing/","title":"Technical writing"}],"subjects":[{"id":"NinjaTrader","path":"/subject/NinjaTrader/","title":"NinjaTrader"}]}},{"node":{"title":"NinjaScript Best Practices - NinjaTrader 8 Help Guide","path":"/content/work/ninja-script-best-practices-ninja-trader-8-help-guid/","date":"June 2016","timeToRead":1,"description":"Over 6-years of work supporting C# developers and the end-users of custom scripts, I accumulated quite a bit of tribal knowledge that was not always clear to end-users how to implement custom scripts to ensure the best performance and maintenance for their users. One of my last assignments for NinjaTrader was compiling a list of common scenarios, gotchas, and workarounds to help optimize the code that was distributed through the ecosystem.","content":"<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1553 1274' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-75f395b288eb3d6a74f7ad98f2adde93'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-75f395b288eb3d6a74f7ad98f2adde93)' width='1553' height='1274' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAA1CAIAAAB%2b5Hr7AAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS